  "about.intro": "My name is ocbot. I'm super smart and super quick at getting things done. I live inside your browser with eight nimble arms ready to handle any task. Ask me to find info, fill forms, compare products, or automate your online work. I don't sleep, I don't forget, and I'm always ready.",
  "about.faq": "FAQ",
  "about.faq1q": "What are you exactly?",
  "about.faq1a": "I'm a new species! Part browser, part AI agent. Think of me as a very helpful octopus that lives in your browser tabs.",
  "about.faq2q": "Why the name \"ocbot\"?",
  "about.faq2a": "Because \"octo\" means 8! I'm an octopus-inspired bot with eight arms ready to multitask across the web.",
  "about.faq3q": "Why purple?",
  "about.faq3a": "Because I'm hitting the big time — only royalty gets to be purple. Plus it's the color of a certain deep-sea creature.",
  "about.faq4q": "Your avatar only has 5 arms.",
  "about.faq4a": "The other 3 are hidden behind me, duh.",
  "about.faq5q": "Will you leak my data?",
  "about.faq5a": "Nope! All your data is stored locally in your browser. I don't phone home. Your conversations, your skills, your settings — all yours.",
